{"word":"ἀπιστέω","slug":"ἀπιστέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀπιστέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄπιστος\">ἄπιστος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘not accept as true, give no credence to’, <b><i>not believe, refuse to believe</i> <a href='B:480 16:11'>Mk 16:11</a>, <a href='B:480 16:16'>16</a>; <a href='B:490 24:11'>Lk 24:11</a>, <a href='B:490 24:41'>41</a>; <a href='B:510 28:24'>Ac 28:24</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ptc.\">ptc.</a> as noun <i>the unbelievers</i><b> <a href='B:670 2:7'>1 Pt 2:7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘lack a sense of obligation/commitment’, <b><i>be unfaithful</i> <a href='B:520 3:3'>Ro 3:3</a>; <a href='B:620 2:13'>2 Ti 2:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπίδω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπιστία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}